# MovieList — `src/components`

## Role

- **Presentational** by default: props in, UI out. **No remote fetching** in dumb/presentational components — parents or hooks supply data.

## Folder layout

- **`src/components/common/`** — components used in **2+ screens** or clearly shared (e.g. `ContentCard`, badges, shared list rows).
- **`src/components/<screen-name>/`** — components **only** for one screen or feature; name the folder after that area (`home`, `detail`, `search`, …).
- **`src/screens/*.tsx`** — compose hooks + components; avoid giant inline JSX; split into **`components/`** when a block grows or could be reused.

## Reusability

- **Extract** to **`common/`** when the same UI pattern appears twice or is likely to (cards, chips, section headers, rating badge).
- **Keep** in **`<screen-name>/`** when behaviour or props are **specific** and unlikely to repeat — do not force abstraction prematurely.
- **Props in, UI out** — presentational; **no TMDB fetching** inside dumb components (parents or hooks pass data).
- Prefer **composition** (small building blocks) over one mega-component file.

## Lists

- Use **`FlatList`** (or **`SectionList`** when needed) for long lists. **Do not add** new list libraries (e.g. FlashList) without explicit approval.

## Styling

- **`StyleSheet.create`**, colours/spacing from **`src/theme/`**. Reuse shared pieces under **`components/common/`** when it reduces duplication.

## Portrait content cards (shared pattern)

- **Aspect ratio:** portrait **2:3** for standard TMDB poster / content cards.
- **Border radius:** **outer** card container **`radiusCardOuter`**; **inner** image masks / nested surfaces **`radiusCardInner`** — from **`src/theme/spacing.ts`** only (no literals in `StyleSheet`).
- **No card-edge border or stroke** — separation via **background/surface** and **spacing** only (no-line rule).
- **Title:** **`title-lg`**, **`on_surface`**, below the image.
- **Subtitle (year • genre):** **`label-sm`**, **`on_surface_variant`**.
- **Rating badge (when shown):** **top-right** overlay on the poster/card area; background **`surface_container_highest`**; star **`primary_container`**; value **`label-sm`**.
- Shared implementations live under **`src/components/common/`** (e.g. **`ContentCard`**) so Home / Search / Watchlist stay consistent.

## Data

- If a component needs TMDB data, the **screen** (or a dedicated hook used only from screens) fetches; pass results as props.

## Testing

- **Do not create** Jest/unit files for presentational UI under **`src/components/**`** (e.g. no `ContentCard.test.tsx`, no co-located `*.test.tsx` next to dumb components). Verify layout in the simulator or via parent screens unless the user **explicitly** asks for component tests.
